Mr. Marc N. Casper has been the Chief Executive Officer and President of Thermo Fisher Scientific, Inc. since October 15, 2009. Mr. Casper has been a Director of Thermo Fisher Scientific, Inc. since October 15, 2009. He served as a Director of Zimmer Holdings, Inc from February 27, 2009 to May 7, 2013. He served as a Director of The Advisory Board Company from February 2003 to September 11, 2009. He served as a Director of Sunol Molecular Corporation. He holds a B.A. in Economics from Wesleyan University, and an M.B.A. with high distinction from Harvard Business School.



